// Write your image in plain words. Optional scopes you can add:
//   $background{ a misty forest at dusk }   = the scene / background
//   $alice{ red dress }, $bob{ blue suit }  = one per subject (keeps them from blending; draw a box in the Region Box panel to place each)
// Lines starting with // are just notes — they are ignored.
