// Design - Poster
A bold graphic poster, large title 'YOUR TITLE' across the top and 'your subtitle here' below, a striking central subject, screen-print texture with flat high-contrast color blocking, strong typographic hierarchy, confident limited palette (color palette #1B1035, #FF2E97, #00E5FF). Portrait 2:3.

// Your description
{cursor}

// Design - Logo / Wordmark
A minimalist flat-vector logo, the wordmark 'BRAND NAME' in clean bold sans-serif with a small simple iconic mark above it, two-tone monochrome palette, perfectly centered with generous whitespace on a plain white background, sharp crisp edges, balanced professional brand mark. 1:1.

// Your description
{cursor}

// Design - Badge / Emblem
A vintage badge emblem with 'EST. 2026' curved along the top and 'YOUR GUILD' curved along the bottom, a central engraving-style icon, distressed letterpress texture, two-tone cream and dark navy, symmetrical centered composition. 1:1.

// Your description
{cursor}

// Design - Album Cover
A square album cover, bold display title 'ALBUM NAME' centered in glowing chrome 3D type, dark gradient background with film grain, dramatic studio lighting and high contrast, color palette #0A0A0A, #00E5FF, #FF2E97. 1:1.

// Your description
{cursor}

// Design - Book Cover
A book cover on a deep navy background (#0D1B2A), a bold centered two-line white title 'THE TITLE' then 'SECOND LINE' with the second line larger, a smaller grey subtitle beneath 'your subtitle', a central minimalist gold geometric illustration, elegant serif typography. Portrait 2:3.

// Your description
{cursor}

// Design - Magazine Cover
A premium magazine cover, large bold masthead 'TITLE' across the top and a smaller tagline 'your tagline' beneath, a striking close-up editorial portrait, dramatic studio lighting with crisp shadows, refined sophisticated palette, clean grid with generous margins, glossy print finish. Portrait 3:4.

// Your description
{cursor}

// Design - Packaging
A product package design, kraft-paper texture background, a centered bold vintage serif name 'PRODUCT NAME' with a small-caps subline 'your descriptor' below, a central hand-drawn engraving-style illustration, warm earthy palette, balanced label layout. 4:5.

// Your description
{cursor}

// Design - Infographic
A clean modern infographic, title 'HOW IT WORKS' with three numbered step labels '1 Create', '2 Convert', '3 Export', simple flat icons, generous white space, a single accent color (color palette #00D1B2, #111111, #FFFFFF), tidy aligned grid. 4:5.

// Your description
{cursor}

// Design - Sticker
A die-cut sticker with a thick clean white border, bold flat cartoon shapes and cheerful saturated colors, a single centered subject, simple chunky linework, an optional all-caps word 'YOUR WORD' in bold condensed type, soft even lighting, glossy vinyl finish. 1:1.

// Your description
{cursor}

// Design - Signage
A modern signage design, the word 'WELCOME' large and centered with a smaller line 'your second line' beneath, high-contrast lettering legible at a glance, clean museum-style layout, simple solid background. 16:9.

// Your description
{cursor}

// Design - Greeting Card
A charming greeting card, a friendly central illustration with a hand-lettered message 'YOUR MESSAGE' above it, soft warm palette, plenty of breathing room, gentle decorative accents, balanced symmetrical layout. Portrait 4:5.

// Your description
{cursor}

// Typography - Bold Headline
Large bold uppercase sans-serif headline reading 'YOUR TEXT', clean crisp letterforms with tight kerning, high-contrast color on a simple flat background, strong centered composition, sharp edges, modern editorial type treatment.

// Your description
{cursor}

// Typography - 3D Inflated Type
Massive puffy inflated 3D balloon letters spelling 'YOUR TEXT', a soft glossy plastic surface with smooth highlights and gentle shadows, playful rounded forms filling the frame, a bright cheerful palette, soft studio lighting.

// Your description
{cursor}

// Typography - Hand-Lettered Script
Elegant hand-lettered script spelling 'YOUR TEXT', flowing brush-pen strokes with graceful flourishes and natural ink texture, a warm cream paper background, refined calligraphic composition, an artisanal feel.

// Your description
{cursor}

// Typography - Neon Sign
A glowing neon sign spelling 'YOUR TEXT' in vibrant cursive tube lighting, a rich magenta-and-cyan glow reflecting on a dark brick wall, soft atmospheric haze, high-contrast night mood, realistic light bloom.

// Your description
{cursor}

// Typography - Vintage Letterpress
Distressed vintage letterpress type spelling 'YOUR TEXT', a bold condensed serif with ink texture and a subtle paper deboss, a muted two-tone palette, a classic centered poster layout, a weathered handcrafted print feel.

// Your description
{cursor}

// Typography - Chrome Display
Sleek liquid-chrome 3D display type spelling 'YOUR TEXT', mirror-polished metal with sharp specular highlights and reflections, a dark gradient background, dramatic rim lighting, a high-gloss futuristic finish.

// Your description
{cursor}

// Illustration - Flat Vector
Designed as flat vector illustration with bold clean outlines, simple geometric shapes and large solid color fills, generous negative space, no gradients or texture, even flat lighting, a minimal modern editorial layout and a confident limited palette.

// Your description
{cursor}

// Illustration - Anime / Manga
Illustrated in clean cel-shaded anime style with confident crisp linework, large expressive eyes and flat vibrant color fills, soft cinematic rim lighting and gentle gradient shadows, Studio Ghibli-inspired warmth, a dynamic three-quarter composition.

// Your description
{cursor}

// Illustration - Comic / Graphic Novel
Drawn in bold comic-book style with heavy black ink outlines, dramatic cross-hatching and crisp cel shading, vivid flat colors with halftone dot texture, a high-contrast dynamic composition and strong directional lighting, graphic-novel ink-and-color energy.

// Your description
{cursor}

// Illustration - Watercolor
Painted in ink and watercolor with fine crisp linework, soft translucent washes that bleed and pool, visible paper texture and granulating pigment, gentle natural light, loose painterly edges, a delicate romantic mood and an airy pastel palette.

// Your description
{cursor}

// Illustration - Oil Painting
Rendered as a textured oil painting with thick visible impasto brushstrokes and rich blended color, warm directional studio light raking across the canvas, deep saturated darks and luminous highlights, a painterly classical composition, an old-master gallery atmosphere.

// Your description
{cursor}

// Illustration - Children's Book
Illustrated in warm storybook style with soft hand-painted gouache textures, rounded friendly shapes and gentle cozy color, soft diffuse daylight, a charming whimsical composition with plenty of breathing room, a tender heartwarming picture-book mood.

// Your description
{cursor}

// Illustration - Concept Art
Rendered as painterly digital concept art with loose confident brushwork and soft atmospheric edges, tonal value blocking, dramatic cinematic lighting and deep aerial perspective, an epic widescreen establishing composition, a moody evocative atmosphere.

// Your description
{cursor}

// Illustration - Fantasy Art
Painted as epic fantasy illustration with luminous golden-hour light and glowing magical accents, a rich jewel-toned palette and intricate ornate detail, a sweeping dramatic vista with atmospheric depth, a heroic awe-inspiring storybook mood.

// Your description
{cursor}

// 3D & Render - 3D Render
Rendered as a polished 3D scene with smooth subsurface-scattered surfaces, soft global illumination and gentle ambient occlusion, glossy and matte material contrast, a dramatic studio key light on a clean gradient backdrop, crisp reflections, high-contrast stylized realism.

// Your description
{cursor}

// 3D & Render - Isometric
Composed as a clean isometric illustration at a true 30-degree angle, a soft pastel palette and smooth vector shading with subtle clay-render volume, even diffuse lighting and gentle long shadows, a tidy miniature-diorama layout on a plain white background.

// Your description
{cursor}

// 3D & Render - Pixel Art
Rendered as crisp 16-bit pixel art on a tight grid, a limited indexed color palette with dithered shading, clean hard-edged sprites and chunky readable forms, flat retro-game lighting, a centered composition against a simple background, a nostalgic arcade mood.

// Your description
{cursor}

// 3D & Render - Clay Figurine
Rendered as a cute claymation figurine sculpted from smooth matte polymer clay, soft rounded handmade forms with gentle fingerprint texture, soft studio lighting on a simple backdrop, a miniature diorama feel, a charming stop-motion look.

// Your description
{cursor}

// Aesthetic - Cyberpunk
Rendered in neon-soaked cyberpunk style with glowing magenta-and-cyan signage reflecting on wet surfaces, dense atmospheric haze and volumetric light, high-contrast darkness pierced by holographic glow, a gritty futuristic city composition, an electric dystopian mood.

// Your description
{cursor}

// Aesthetic - Minimalist
Composed as a clean minimalist design with a single subject and abundant negative space, a soft gradient or solid background, a restrained two-or-three-color palette, flat even lighting, precise balanced placement, an elegant calm uncluttered mood.

// Your description
{cursor}

// Aesthetic - Synthwave / Retro
Rendered in 1980s synthwave style with a glowing neon grid horizon and a setting-sun gradient, chrome accents and purple-and-pink haze, bold retro-futuristic composition, scanline texture, a nostalgic outrun mood. Color palette #1B1035, #FF2E97, #00E5FF.

// Your description
{cursor}

// Aesthetic - Risograph / Screenprint
Rendered as a risograph screen-print with a limited 2-3 ink palette, grainy halftone texture and slight misregistration, bold flat shapes with overprint blends, matte paper feel, a handmade indie-poster aesthetic.
